<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Conet Registration</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/img/logo2.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/registerStyle.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5 mx-auto">
        <div class="card card0">
            <div class="d-flex flex-lg-row flex-column-reverse">
                <div class="card card1">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center my-auto">
                        <div class="col-md-8 col-10 my-5">
                            <div class="row justify-content-center px-3 mb-3"></div>
                            <h3 class="mb-5 text-center heading" style="font-family: Aclonica;">JOIN THE CO-NET
                                COMMUNITY</h3>
                            <h5 class="msg-info">Kindly Fill Out The Form</h5>
                            <% if (error) { %>
                            <h6 style="color: white; background-color: red; padding: 10px">
                              <%= error %>
                            </h6>
                            <% } %> <% if (message) { %>
                            <h6
                              style="color: white; background-color: green; padding: 10px"
                            >
                              <%= message %>
                            </h6>
                            <% } %>
                            <form method="POST">
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Name</label>
                                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="" class="form-control" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Phone Number</label>
                                <input type="text" id="phonenumber" name="phoneNumber" placeholder=""
                                    class="form-control" required> </div>
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Email</label>
                                <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="" class="form-control" required> </div>
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Native Place</label>
                                <input type="test" id="nativePlace" name="nativePlace" placeholder="" class="form-control" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Area of
                                    expertise</label>
                                <input type="text" id="areaOfExpertise" name="areaOfExpertise" placeholder=""
                                    class="form-control" required></input>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">What Describes
                                    You</label>
                                <select class="form-control" id="description" name="description" required>
                                    <option>Choose Option</option>
                                    <option value="Freelance Trainer">Freelance Trainer</option>
                                    <option value="Part of a Training Organization">Part of a Training Organization
                                    </option>
                                    <option value="College Faculty">College Faculty</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group"> <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Any Suggestions to Add
                                    Up?</label>
                                <textarea type="text" id="suggestion" name="suggestion" placeholder=""
                                    class="form-control" required></textarea> </div>

                            <div class="row justify-content-center my-3 px-3"> <button type="submit"
                                    class="btn-block btn-color">Register
                                </button> </div>
                              </form>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card card2">
                    <div class="my-auto mx-md-5 px-md-5 right">
                        <h3 class="text-white">CoNet with Conex!</h3> <br><small class="text-white"
                            style="font-size: 18px;">We want talented trainers to step forward and enlighten our target
                            audiences. This knowledge has the capacity to change the world and help our young
                            professionals support their families and aid in this economic crisis.
                            Be the member of the highly respected and dynamic panel team. Exchange knowledge, spread
                            astuteness and also reap the various benefits. Meet people from national and international
                            platforms, network, train the ambitious gems that are ignored by the Industry and stretch
                            your own learning curve as well.
                            CoNet with Conex! We promise to add value to your life!<br><b>
                                Fill in the form and we promise to be in touch within 12hrs!</b></small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</html>
